title: RESTART_FRONTEND_MENU
content:
0x10706DC6AD2D49C00xB07DAF98// RestartFrontendMenu
void RESTART_FRONTEND_MENU(Hash menuHash, int highlightedTab);Parameters:menuHash: Hash of the frontend menu. See ACTIVATE_FRONTEND_MENU for the list of available menus.highlightedTab: Menu ID (from PauseMenuLUT (in pause_menu_sp_content.gfx files), but the value - 1000) of which tab to have highlighted on the header, or -1.Changes the current frontend menu to the desired frontend menu version.
